videos.description: Boogie Ellis makes a nice pass to D.J. Jeffries, who finishes with the slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Jeffries elevates for wide-open slam) 2020/01/25

videos.headline: Jeffries elevates for wide-open slam

videos.description: With less than two minutes remaining in the second half, Isiaha Mike hits a deep 3-pointer to give SMU a one-point lead, their first lead since the first two minutes of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Mike knocks in 3 to give SMU late lead) 2020/01/25

videos.headline: Mike knocks in 3 to give SMU late lead

videos.description: Memphis' Precious Achiuwa steals the ball and attempts a 3-pointer, but he misses it and SMU goes on to win 74-70.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Achiuwa misses game-tying 3 for Memphis) 2020/01/25

videos.headline: Achiuwa misses game-tying 3 for Memphis
